---
import OtherHero from '../banners/OtherHero.astro';
---

<s_article_protected>
  <s_permalink_article_rep>
    <OtherHero
      title="[##_article_rep_title_##]"
      desc="[##_article_rep_category_##]"
      imgSrc="[##_article_rep_thumbnail_url_##]"
    />
    <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto text-center">
      <div
        class="mb-8 pt-50 background-[url(./images/icon-exclamation.svg)] bg-center bg-top bg-no-repeat text-base"
      >
        <p class="">
          보호되어 있는 글입니다. <br />
          <span class="text-base h-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            내용을 보시려면 비밀번호를 입력하세요.
          </span>
        </p>
        <form class="protected_form" onsubmit=`[##_article_dissolve_##]`>
          <div class="box-protected">
            <input
              type="password"
              id="[##_article_password_##]"
              name="[##_article_password_##]"
              value=""
              placeholder="비밀번호"
              class="w-full h-20 mb-4 text-sm pl-8 border rounded-full focus:outline-none"
            />
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="block w-full h-20 bg-gray-300 text-base dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-400 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition duration-300 text-black dark:text-white"
            >
              확인
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </s_permalink_article_rep>
</s_article_protected>
